We’ve been keeping a little secret..
Bryancito is going to be a big brother 🕊

Photo dump 📸🤰🏻

 I feel so emotional that this journey is coming to an end. I can’t believe I’ll have my baby in my arms in just a few weeks. I feel so so blessed. Thank you God.

Our sweet Noah,
We can’t wait to meet you 🤍

Just counting down the days now…🤎
@mayamurophotography 

I’ve been feeling very emotional. I can’t believe we’ve got this far. Thank you God. 
#37weekspregnant

I couldn’t have asked for a better partner to go through this journey with. For better, for worse. We are standing by the grace of God. I would do anything to go back in time and tell my broken self how strong she really is. These past couple years tested every bone in me. I felt my life was over. I had no purpose. I felt defeated. Here we are today about to have our second baby boy. My sweet Noah, we love you so much. You’ve changed our life. You gave us purpose again. You gave us light. And for my papa, my first born, my beautiful boy. Words will never express the love I have for you. Your my best friend. My soulmate. My world. I wish so badly you were here to see it all. You’d be the best big brother ever. Our family will never feel complete without you. I miss you more and more everyday. Mommy is staying strong until we meet again. 
_____________________________

Thank you @mayamurophotography for these beautiful images🤎

To the little boy who saved me 🤍

Noah Bryan Renteria
Born April 8th, 2023 at 10:43am
Weighing 8lbs 0.4oz | 20in
